{"article_id":"lJ8CemkBKHzkSqvG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"TOKYO/WASHINGTON","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo brushed off North Korean charges","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"that he used \" gangster-like \" diplomacy in negotiations in Pyongyang ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"saying on Sunday","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"after meeting his Japanese and South Korean counterparts","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"that he would keep pursuing denuclearization talks with North Korea .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"in Tokyo","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"there was still a lot of work to do ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"but he was confident","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"North Korean leader Kim Jong Un would stick to a commitment","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"to abandon nuclear weapons","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"he made during a summit with U.S. President Donald Trump in Singapore last month .","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"\" When we spoke to them about denuclearization ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"they did not push back , \"","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"Pompeo told a news conference after two days of talks in Pyongyang","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"that ended on Saturday .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"\" The road ahead will be difficult and challenging","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"and we know","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that critics will try to minimize the work","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"that we ' ve achieved . \"","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Some U.S. senators expressed concern about North Korea ' s harsh words","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and urged the Trump administration to keep up the pressure on Pyongyang .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Republican Senator Joni Ernst , a member of the Armed Services Committee , said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"joint military exercises with South Korea","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"suspended","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"to show goodwill toward North Korea","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"should be resumed \" soon \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"if talks sputter .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"while he saw progress in Pyongyang ,","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"the United States was not relaxing the current sanctions regime","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"or changing its \" ironclad \" commitment","depth":16},{"id":35,"text":"to defend allies South Korea and Japan .","depth":16},{"id":36,"text":"Pompeo spoke","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"after North Korea said","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"the talks \" brought us in a dangerous situation","depth":15},{"id":39,"text":"where we may be shaken in our unshakable will for denuclearization ,","depth":16},{"id":40,"text":"rather than consolidating trust . \"","depth":16},{"id":41,"text":"The statement was carried by the official KCNA news agency on Saturday","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"soon after Pompeo left Pyongyang ,","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"raising questions about the future of talks","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"in which he is trying to persuade Pyongyang to give up a nuclear weapons program","depth":16},{"id":45,"text":"that threatens the United States .","depth":16},{"id":46,"text":"\" That was a fairly serious insult","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"directed against Pompeo , \"","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"said Christopher Hill ,","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"who formerly served as U.S. ambassador to South Korea and lead negotiator with North Korea .","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"Kim made a broad commitment in Singapore","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"to \" work toward denuclearization \"","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"but did not give details","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"on how or when he would dismantle North Korea ' s nuclear program .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"Trump offered security guarantees to Pyongyang","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and pledged to suspend the large-scale military drills with South Korea .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Leaked U.S. intelligence findings have concluded","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that North Korea does not intend to give up its nuclear program completely .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"North Korea ' s latest comments were a reminder of the difficulties","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"that previous U.S. administrations had negotiating with the reclusive state .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"it was a pretty bad start to the process ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"but it doesn ' t mean it ' s over yet , \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"said Hill ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that North Korea talks were tough by nature .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"\" Most of the time you don ' t come back with anything .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Most of the time you come back empty-handed , \"","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Hill added .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"he did not meet Kim on his latest visit to Pyongyang ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"as he had twice before ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"and he had not anticipated doing so .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"The White House said before the trip","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that he would meet Kim .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"In a speech on Sunday in Vietnam , Pompeo urged North Korea to follow the example of Vietnam ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"he believed","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Pyongyang could replicate Hanoi ' s path to normal relations with Washington and to prosperity .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"\" The United States has been clear on what we seek from North Korea , \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Pompeo said in Hanoi .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"\" The choice now lies with North Korea and its people .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"\" If they are able to do this ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"they will be remembered ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"and Chairman Kim will be remembered , as a hero of the Korean people . \"","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo , Japan 's Foreign Minister Taro Kono and South Korea 's Foreign Minister Kang Kyung Wha shake hands for members of the media","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"as they meet in Tokyo , Japan , July 8 , 2018 .","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"Andrew Harnik/Pool via","depth":4},{"id":88,"text":"Some analysts and lawmakers have expressed alarm","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that the talks appear to have run into difficulties ,","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"although others see a possible North Korean negotiating ploy .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"\" I see China ' s hands all over this , \"","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"said Republican Senator Lindsey Graham ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"he thought","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"the Chinese were \" pulling back \" North Korea","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"because of the U.S.-China trade dispute .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Richard Haass , president of the Council on Foreign Relations , said on Twitter","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"there was a danger of military action","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"because Trump might now say","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"he had tried diplomacy","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"but was betrayed by Kim .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"\" But a rushed summit and demands","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that NK denuclearize in short order","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"or else","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"is not a serious test of diplomacy , \"","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Haass tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"South Korean Foreign Minister Kang Kyung-wha said","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"her country did not believe","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Washington had softened its demands ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"as some U.S. officials and analysts have suggested .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"\" Secretary Pompeo ' s visit to Pyongyang this time has taken the first steps , \"","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"\" We expect this to be followed up by further constructive and productive negotiations . \"","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"After he met Japanese Minister of Foreign Affairs Taro Kono ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"he was in Tokyo","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"to discuss the U.S. alliance with Japan","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"and maintaining \" maximum pressure \" on North Korea , an expression","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"Trump ' s administration had backed away from after the Singapore summit .","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"he had pushed North Korea on a promise","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"to destroy a missile engine test site .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"He also said","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"talks had yielded an agreement","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"to form a \" working-level \" group","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"to oversee day-to-day interactions between the United States and North Korea .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Officials from the two sides would meet next week in Panmunjom , on the border between the two Koreas ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"to discuss the return of the remains of roughly 7,000 U.S. soldiers","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"missing since the 1950-1953 Korean War .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"KCNA said","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Pyongyang had offered to discuss declaring a formal end to the war","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"to mark next month ' s anniversary of the armistice .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"It said","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"the U.S. side had shown little interest ,","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"giving \" certain conditions and excuses . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":0,"right":270,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":219,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":1,"right":218,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":218,"left":202,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":191,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":155,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":140,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":137,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":138,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":138,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":146,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":142,"right":145,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":7,"right":141,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":10,"right":144,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":143,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":149,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":18,"right":151,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":19,"right":150,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":162,"right":189,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{